Author:
oytun.turk A MaryEffectControl consists of a checkbox, a text pane, a text field, and a button The checkbox indicates whether the effect will be applied or not The label contains the name of the effect The text field contains the parameters of the effect The button shows help information about the usage of the effect when clicked
